com.b2international.snowowl.datastore.cdo

Class CDOViewFunction<T,V extends org.eclipse.emf.cdo.view.CDOView>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.b2international.snowowl.datastore.cdo.CDOViewFunction<T,V>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    CDOFunction<T>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    CDOTransactionFunction

    public abstract class CDOViewFunction<T,V extends org.eclipse.emf.cdo.view.CDOView>
extends Object
implements CDOFunction<T>
    Function for performing an operation on an underlying view.

    It's advantage is that the client should not take care about releasing the underlying resource.
